Class DBProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sb.db.cassandra.DBProperties

  • public class DBProperties
extends Object
    This class is used to set the database required properties. It is a common class for setting up jdbc or ds properties (refer TestCassandraDB for implementation)

    bizz.sand
